  "description": "Calm synthetic Movora-branded codec probe clips. No copyrighted footage, no third-party artwork, no music samples. Base clips are generated externally; the container/resolution/HDR/audio variants are derived with ffmpeg (see README.md). Covers real-world cases: anime (Hi10P, FLAC/Opus), 4K HEVC/HDR remux, and lossless/multichannel audio. The video_codec/video_bit_depth/audio_codec/container fields drive profile_from_report (movora.compat): a played video/container sample marks that codec+bit-depth token and container as supported; an audible audio sample marks that audio codec supported.",
